Privacy Policy
At PITBALL, your privacy is a priority for us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you interact with our services. By using our application, you agree to the practices described below.

1. Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of personal information depending on your interaction with our services:

Names
Phone numbers
Email addresses
Passwords
Sensitive Information:
With your consent, or as otherwise permitted by applicable law, we may collect sensitive data, including:

Student data
Biometric data
Application Data:
We may request access to certain features of your mobile device to ensure proper operation of the app. This may include:

Camera access
Storage access
Internet access
You can manage these permissions in your device's settings.
2. How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information to:

Provide and improve our services
Maintain the security and operation of the application
Perform troubleshooting and analytics
3. Data Security
We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to secure your personal data against unauthorized access or misuse.

4. Your Rights
You may update, correct, or delete your personal data by contacting us at mahmudesadbuyuk@gmail.com.

